{
  "title": "ws telemetry",
  "uid": "ws-telemetry",
  "tags": ["ws", "observaloop"],
  "timezone": "browser",
  "schemaVersion": 39,
  "version": 2,
  "editable": true,
  "refresh": "30s",
  "time": { "from": "now-30m", "to": "now" },
  "templating": {
    "list": [
      {
        "name": "ws_rig",
        "label": "rig",
        "type": "query",
        "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus" },
        "query": "label_values(ws_rig)",
        "allValue": ".*",
        "includeAll": true,
        "multi": true,
        "current": { "text": "All", "value": "$__all" }
      },
      {
        "name": "ws_worktree",
        "label": "worktree",
        "type": "query",
        "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus" },
        "query": "label_values(ws_worktree)",
        "allValue": ".*",
        "includeAll": true,
        "multi": true,
        "current": { "text": "All", "value": "$__all" }
      }
    ]
  },
  "annotations": { "list": [] },
  "__comment_metric_names": "PromQL below queries the OTLP instruments from ws/otel.py as ingested by the otel-lgtm Prometheus: dots->underscores, counters gain _total, second-unit histograms gain _seconds and a _bucket series. Source instruments: ws.cli.invocations, ws.cli.duration, ws.mcp.tool.invocations, ws.mcp.tool.duration, ws.errors. Resource/attribute labels: ws.rig, ws.worktree, observaloop.profile, ws.cli.command, ws.cli.outcome, ws.mcp.tool, ws.error.boundary, ws.error.kind.",
  "panels": [
    {
      "id": 1,
      "type": "row",
      "title": "RED — ws CLI (ws.cli.*)",
      "collapsed": false,
      "gridPos": { "h": 1, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 0 }
    },
    {
      "id": 2,
      "type": "timeseries",
      "title": "CLI invocation rate — ws.cli.invocations by command",
      "description": "Rate (R of RED) of CLI command entries, split by ws.cli.command.",
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus" },
      "gridPos": { "h": 8, "w": 8, "x": 0, "y": 1 },
      "fieldConfig": { "defaults": { "unit": "reqps" }, "overrides": [] },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus" },
          "expr": "sum by (ws_cli_command) (rate(ws_cli_invocations_total{ws_rig=~\"$ws_rig\", ws_worktree=~\"$ws_worktree\"}[$__rate_interval]))",
          "legendFormat": "{{ws_cli_command}}"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 3,
      "type": "timeseries",
      "title": "CLI error rate — ws.cli.invocations{ws.cli.outcome=error}",
      "description": "Errors (E of RED) from the CLI invocation counter tagged ws.cli.outcome=error.",
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus" },
      "gridPos": { "h": 8, "w": 8, "x": 8, "y": 1 },
      "fieldConfig": { "defaults": { "unit": "reqps" }, "overrides": [] },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus" },
          "expr": "sum by (ws_cli_command) (rate(ws_cli_invocations_total{ws_cli_outcome=\"error\", ws_rig=~\"$ws_rig\", ws_worktree=~\"$ws_worktree\"}[$__rate_interval]))",
          "legendFormat": "{{ws_cli_command}}"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 4,
      "type": "timeseries",
      "title": "CLI duration p95 — ws.cli.duration",
      "description": "Duration (D of RED) p95 wall time per CLI command from the ws.cli.duration histogram.",
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus" },
      "gridPos": { "h": 8, "w": 8, "x": 16, "y": 1 },
      "fieldConfig": { "defaults": { "unit": "s" }, "overrides": [] },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus" },
          "expr": "histogram_quantile(0.95, sum by (le, ws_cli_command) (rate(ws_cli_duration_seconds_bucket{ws_rig=~\"$ws_rig\", ws_worktree=~\"$ws_worktree\"}[$__rate_interval])))",
          "legendFormat": "{{ws_cli_command}}"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 5,
      "type": "row",
      "title": "RED — ws MCP tools (ws.mcp.tool.*)",
      "collapsed": false,
      "gridPos": { "h": 1, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 9 }
    },
    {
      "id": 6,
      "type": "timeseries",
      "title": "MCP tool invocation rate — ws.mcp.tool.invocations by tool",
      "description": "Rate of MCP tool calls, split by ws.mcp.tool (ok+error via ws.mcp.outcome).",
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus" },
      "gridPos": { "h": 8, "w": 12, "x": 0, "y": 10 },
      "fieldConfig": { "defaults": { "unit": "reqps" }, "overrides": [] },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus" },
          "expr": "sum by (ws_mcp_tool, ws_mcp_outcome) (rate(ws_mcp_tool_invocations_total{ws_rig=~\"$ws_rig\"}[$__rate_interval]))",
          "legendFormat": "{{ws_mcp_tool}} ({{ws_mcp_outcome}})"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 7,
      "type": "timeseries",
      "title": "MCP tool duration p95 — ws.mcp.tool.duration",
      "description": "p95 wall time per MCP tool from the ws.mcp.tool.duration histogram.",
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus" },
      "gridPos": { "h": 8, "w": 12, "x": 12, "y": 10 },
      "fieldConfig": { "defaults": { "unit": "s" }, "overrides": [] },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus" },
          "expr": "histogram_quantile(0.95, sum by (le, ws_mcp_tool) (rate(ws_mcp_tool_duration_seconds_bucket{ws_rig=~\"$ws_rig\"}[$__rate_interval])))",
          "legendFormat": "{{ws_mcp_tool}}"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 8,
      "type": "row",
      "title": "Errors (ws.errors)",
      "collapsed": false,
      "gridPos": { "h": 1, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 18 }
    },
    {
      "id": 9,
      "type": "timeseries",
      "title": "Unhandled errors — ws.errors by boundary + kind",
      "description": "Unhandled errors at instrumented boundaries, split by ws.error.boundary and ws.error.kind.",
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus" },
      "gridPos": { "h": 8, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 19 },
      "fieldConfig": { "defaults": { "unit": "reqps" }, "overrides": [] },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus" },
          "expr": "sum by (ws_error_boundary, ws_error_kind) (rate(ws_errors_total{ws_rig=~\"$ws_rig\", ws_worktree=~\"$ws_worktree\"}[$__rate_interval]))",
          "legendFormat": "{{ws_error_boundary}} / {{ws_error_kind}}"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 10,
      "type": "row",
      "title": "Traces — ws.cli root (trace nesting)",
      "collapsed": false,
      "gridPos": { "h": 1, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 27 }
    },
    {
      "id": 11,
      "type": "table",
      "title": "ws.cli root spans — the per-invocation trace root",
      "description": "The `ws.cli {command}` root span every trace_verb + subprocess span nests under (see ws/cli.py).",
      "datasource": { "type": "tempo", "uid": "tempo" },
      "gridPos": { "h": 9, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 28 },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "datasource": { "type": "tempo", "uid": "tempo" },
          "queryType": "traceql",
          "query": "{ name =~ \"ws.cli.*\" }",
          "limit": 50,
          "tableType": "traces"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 12,
      "type": "row",
      "title": "Per-worktree breakdown (ws.worktree / observaloop.profile / ws.rig)",
      "collapsed": false,
      "gridPos": { "h": 1, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 36 }
    },
    {
      "id": 13,
      "type": "table",
      "title": "CLI invocations by worktree — ws.worktree / observaloop.profile / ws.rig",
      "description": "Per-worktree breakdown using ws.rig, ws.worktree, and observaloop.profile as series labels promoted by the CLI-metrics preset. Requires ws rig init --observaloop (preset + delta temporality); trace panels work without the preset.",
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus" },
      "gridPos": { "h": 8, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 37 },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "format": "table",
          "instant": true,
          "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus" },
          "expr": "sum by (ws_rig, ws_worktree, observaloop_profile) (rate(ws_cli_invocations_total{ws_rig=~\"$ws_rig\", ws_worktree=~\"$ws_worktree\"}[$__rate_interval]))"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 14,
      "type": "row",
      "title": "AGF lifecycle (ws.work.*)",
      "collapsed": false,
      "gridPos": { "h": 1, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 45 }
    },
    {
      "id": 15,
      "type": "timeseries",
      "title": "Bead transitions — ws.work.bead.transitions by transition",
      "description": "Rate of bead-lifecycle transitions (assigned, claimed, abandoned, review_pending, merged, molecule_landed) from ws.work.bead.transitions, split by ws.bead.transition.",
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus" },
      "gridPos": { "h": 8, "w": 6, "x": 0, "y": 46 },
      "fieldConfig": { "defaults": { "unit": "reqps" }, "overrides": [] },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus" },
          "expr": "sum by (ws_bead_transition) (rate(ws_work_bead_transitions_total{ws_rig=~\"$ws_rig\", ws_worktree=~\"$ws_worktree\"}[$__rate_interval]))",
          "legendFormat": "{{ws_bead_transition}}"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 16,
      "type": "timeseries",
      "title": "Merge duration p50/p95 — ws.work.merge.duration by kind",
      "description": "Bead vs molecule merge wall-time (p50 + p95) from ws.work.merge.duration, split by ws.merge.kind (bead|molecule).",
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus" },
      "gridPos": { "h": 8, "w": 6, "x": 6, "y": 46 },
      "fieldConfig": { "defaults": { "unit": "s" }, "overrides": [] },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus" },
          "expr": "histogram_quantile(0.50, sum by (le, ws_merge_kind) (rate(ws_work_merge_duration_seconds_bucket{ws_rig=~\"$ws_rig\", ws_worktree=~\"$ws_worktree\"}[$__rate_interval])))",
          "legendFormat": "p50 {{ws_merge_kind}}"
        },
        {
          "refId": "B",
          "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus" },
          "expr": "histogram_quantile(0.95, sum by (le, ws_merge_kind) (rate(ws_work_merge_duration_seconds_bucket{ws_rig=~\"$ws_rig\", ws_worktree=~\"$ws_worktree\"}[$__rate_interval])))",
          "legendFormat": "p95 {{ws_merge_kind}}"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 17,
      "type": "timeseries",
      "title": "Validation pass/fail — ws.work.validation.runs by result",
      "description": "Rate of validation runs (pass|fail) from ws.work.validation.runs, split by ws.validation.result and ws.work.phase (check|submit|molecule).",
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus" },
      "gridPos": { "h": 8, "w": 6, "x": 12, "y": 46 },
      "fieldConfig": { "defaults": { "unit": "reqps" }, "overrides": [] },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus" },
          "expr": "sum by (ws_validation_result, ws_work_phase) (rate(ws_work_validation_runs_total{ws_rig=~\"$ws_rig\", ws_worktree=~\"$ws_worktree\"}[$__rate_interval]))",
          "legendFormat": "{{ws_validation_result}} / {{ws_work_phase}}"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 18,
      "type": "table",
      "title": "Agent dispatch spans — invoke_agent (GenAI)",
      "description": "The GenAI invoke_agent spans emitted by record_agent_dispatch when the coordinator hands a bead to a developer crew. Queried from Tempo via TraceQL; gen_ai.agent.name identifies the crew.",
      "datasource": { "type": "tempo", "uid": "tempo" },
      "gridPos": { "h": 8, "w": 6, "x": 18, "y": 46 },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "datasource": { "type": "tempo", "uid": "tempo" },
          "queryType": "traceql",
          "query": "{ name =~ \"invoke_agent.*\" }",
          "limit": 50,
          "tableType": "traces"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 19,
      "type": "row",
      "title": "Worktree events (ws.worktree.events)",
      "collapsed": false,
      "gridPos": { "h": 1, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 54 }
    },
    {
      "id": 20,
      "type": "timeseries",
      "title": "Worktree events — ws.worktree.events by op + outcome",
      "description": "Rate of worktree lifecycle events (create|remove|prune) from ws.worktree.events, split by ws.worktree.op and ws.worktree.outcome (ok|error). Scoped by $ws_rig/$ws_worktree so a fixture run is visible in isolation.",
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus" },
      "gridPos": { "h": 8, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 55 },
      "fieldConfig": { "defaults": { "unit": "reqps" }, "overrides": [] },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus" },
          "expr": "sum by (ws_worktree_op, ws_worktree_outcome) (rate(ws_worktree_events_total{ws_rig=~\"$ws_rig\", ws_worktree=~\"$ws_worktree\"}[$__rate_interval]))",
          "legendFormat": "{{ws_worktree_op}} / {{ws_worktree_outcome}}"
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}
